skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: palm coast
Developer Terms of Use
des:
Get connected to be the ultimate Palm Coaster. Discover the latest of what’s going on in our city just by the sound of your voice. 

In the Palm Coast app, you can ask Alexa, “What’s the latest announcements?”, “What day is my garbage day?”, "Play City Council Meeting.”, or "Report a Concern"
